Package: simK
Title: Simulation of Kidney Transplantation Synthetic Data 
Version: 0.1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Bruno", "Lima", , "balima78@gmauil.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9090-4457"))
Description: Functions to generate simulated data for cadaveric donors and kidney transplant candidates. 
    Includes HLA typing data previously puiblished [Lima et al, 2013]<ref: https://www.slideshare.net/balima78/lima-2013>.
    Particularly useful to generate datasets to run in KARS.  
